03ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLakeborne Shotgun\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-3.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-3\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$7500\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eCommon\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 10\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e6\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e300\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.45s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e75%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLakeborne Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-4.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-4\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$12500\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eUncommon\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 15\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e12\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e400\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e400\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.35s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e90%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n    \u003ch3 id=\"h-mount-beaks-area-guns\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eMount Beaks Area Guns\u003c/h3\u003e    \u003cfigure data-current-count=\"300\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-mount-beak-path.jpg?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-mount-beak-path\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot by The Escapist.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"375\" data-current-count=\"675\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003eThe best way to access this area is to \u003cstrong\u003edrop down from the spawnpoint\u003c/strong\u003e and go \u003cstrong\u003edirectly to your left\u003c/strong\u003e. There’s\u003cstrong\u003e another stone path\u003c/strong\u003e that can help you out, but the moment you drop down in the woods you’ll see the \u003cstrong\u003eMount Beaks area sign\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003cstrong\u003eClimbing up the mountain\u003c/strong\u003e is easier than it looks, and once you\u003cstrong\u003e take the first right off the path \u003c/strong\u003eyou’ve arrived to the\u003cstrong\u003e heart of Mount Beaks\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cfigure data-current-count=\"300\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-mount-beak.jpg?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-mount-beak\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot by The Escapist.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"373\" data-current-count=\"673\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003eHere you’ll find \u003cstrong\u003eFlint\u003c/strong\u003e, who can get you\u003cstrong\u003e access to two new guns\u003c/strong\u003e, stronger and more precise than the previous ones. Of course, this strength comes at a\u003cstrong\u003e significantly steeper price both in money and the tediousness of climbing\u003c/strong\u003e, but Mount Beaks is arguably the \u003cstrong\u003ebest position on the map to hunt birds \u003c/strong\u003ebecause of its altitude. These two guns can help you out in that endeavour:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cfigure data-found-rows=\"2\" data-current-count=\"380\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eAppearance\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003ePrice\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eRarity\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel Requirement\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eDamage Per Hit\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eRange\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eSpeed\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eFire Rate\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eAccuracy\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMt. Beaks Long-Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-5.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-5\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$25000\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eUncommon\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 20\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e16\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e1000\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e400\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.3s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e85%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSummit Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-6.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-6\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$17000\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eRare\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 25\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e12\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e750\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e650\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.4s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e85%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"h-deadlands-area-guns\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eDeadlands Area Guns\u003c/h3\u003e    \u003cfigure data-current-count=\"680\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-deadlands-sign.jpg?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-deadlands-sign\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot by The Escapist.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cp data-characters=\"458\" data-current-count=\"458\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003eRemember that \u003cstrong\u003efirst path from the spawnpoint\u003c/strong\u003e? This is where you need to be in order to unlock the last area on the map.\u003cstrong\u003e Follow the stone path once you cross the lake \u003c/strong\u003eand go\u003cstrong\u003e all the way until its end\u003c/strong\u003e. When you reach the \u003cstrong\u003eDeadlands sign\u003c/strong\u003e, you’ll see a\u003cstrong\u003e vast area beneath you\u003c/strong\u003e. You can \u003cstrong\u003ego to your right \u003c/strong\u003ewhere you’ll find another area sign and \u003cstrong\u003edescend down the stairs\u003c/strong\u003e – or, you know, \u003cstrong\u003ejust jump off the vantage point\u003c/strong\u003e. There’s no dying in this game anyway.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n        \u003cp data-characters=\"356\" data-current-count=\"356\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eOnce you’re\u003cstrong\u003e down in the heart of Deadlands\u003c/strong\u003e, you need to\u003cstrong\u003e go to the left\u003c/strong\u003e. Pass the weird scientist making a skeleton bird, pass the green fumes, \u003cstrong\u003ekeep left all the way until you reach the very end of the path\u003c/strong\u003e, where you’ll find \u003cstrong\u003eCommander Thorne\u003c/strong\u003e, the gun merchant, \u003cstrong\u003einside the sole house\u003c/strong\u003e. He can sell you the\u003cstrong\u003e two strongest (and most expensive) guns\u003c/strong\u003e in-game:\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cfigure data-found-rows=\"2\" data-current-count=\"736\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eAppearance\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003ePrice\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eRarity\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel Requirement\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eDamage Per Hit\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eRange\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eSpeed\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eFire Rate\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth data-align=\"center\"\u003eAccuracy\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDeadlands Long-Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-7.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-7\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$37500\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eEpic\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 30\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e20\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e900\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e650\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.45s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e85%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eViper Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/beaks-all-guns-8.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"beaks-all-guns-8\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e$55000\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLegendary\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003eLevel 35\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e25\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e750\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e500\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e0.4s\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e91%\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cp data-characters=\"250\" data-current-count=\"250\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAnd that’s how to find all guns in \u003cem\u003eBeaks\u003c/em\u003e. Choose whichever works best for you and collect the rarest birds with ease. Looking to chat to fellow players? Check out our \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/official-beaks-trello-and-discord/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eBeaks \u003c/em\u003eTrello \u0026amp; Discord server links\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e for all social links related to the game.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003